Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:26.84,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ride on that wind, and spread your wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:36.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody knows that I can see Youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:39.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an umbrella flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.32,0:01:41.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,An umbrella?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.52,0:01:42.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.53,0:01:44.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.22,0:01:45.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you say it was? Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:48.42,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:55.67,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it must've been a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:56.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.31,0:01:58.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:01:59.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:00.42,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:14.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see me, human child?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.71,0:02:24.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me tell you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.46,0:02:28.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to touch any humans, but I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:33.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Your body is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:34.46,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:37.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:40.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:42.93,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:54.33,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really short-tempered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.33,0:02:56.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyanko-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:03:00.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There's some calcium, so eat it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:02.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:06.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, how careless of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:09.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty good for a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:12.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'll have that body by any means!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:14.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:16.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Akagane.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.51,0:03:19.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Human child, please forgive his rudeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:22.91,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it all for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:24.93,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a voice coming from the gourd.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:28.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk, Asagi. You'll get tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:30.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:43.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:47.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Asagi... I've heard that name before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:52.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an illusionary city where nobles gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:58.92,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Some say that there's a beautiful koto player named Asagi in Isozuki Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:02.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's {\i1}that{\i0} Asagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:03.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:06.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,However, she fell ill and became unable to play the koto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:08.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She was forced to go back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:11.15,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She used to laugh often, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.70,0:04:13.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Then suddenly, she became unwell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:20.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So, human child, for Asagi's sake, lend that body...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.91,0:04:26.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't listen to me, I'll bite off your ears and nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:27.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:28.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, you shrimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.33,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:34.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A raccoon dog bit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:35.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:37.54,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't laugh, Jizou!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:41.55,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing good comes from carelessly getting involved with Ayakashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:44.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And even worse, lending them your body?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.53,0:04:48.59,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She used to often laugh, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.66,0:04:50.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:54.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of pitied them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.98,0:05:06.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.71,0:05:10.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Nyanko-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.34,0:05:12.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming back in the morning again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:16.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume, your hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:21.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes are kind of blue as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.46,0:05:26.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:29.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it just my imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:34.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:36.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.59,0:05:40.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.01,0:05:47.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Morning, Kitamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:51.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That surprised me. I thought I had the wrong person for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:54.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ew, what's with those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:52.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:05:57.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:00.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the dictionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:02.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.44,0:06:05.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:11.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You dropped it, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:22.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Tanuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:25.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Tanuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.09,0:06:31.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I thought you were a girl for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:34.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I just imagined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:37.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:41.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving Kitamoto aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:44.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,if Tanuma could feel something, then could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:56.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You did something, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:07:00.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I placed Asagi inside your body while you were sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:04.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she's adapting to you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.87,0:07:07.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I pray that you'll cooperate for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.71,0:07:16.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So the blue hair and eyes from this morning were the manifestation of being possessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:18.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:21.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him to stop,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:25.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,but I had no way to control myself. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:29.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This voice... You're Asagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:31.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't blame him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.36,0:07:35.54,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:38.10,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, you don't need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:41.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:47.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A way to get her out of your body?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:49.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, something not too violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:54.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then you have no choice but to grant Asagi's wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:58.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,When she feels satisfied, I'm sure she'll leave your body naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:01.25,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But her wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:03.75,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:07.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and finish this so we can go back, human child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:08.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be the one talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:11.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you come from? What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:14.93,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give my name to mere humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:17.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Then your name is Bullseye from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:19.55,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,After the bullseye from a bullseye-patterned umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:21.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bullseye?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:24.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming to pick us up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.79,0:08:26.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Damned raccoon dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.29,0:08:28.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, what a cute name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:30.92,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad, Bullseye?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:32.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Even you too, Asagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:37.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, isn't it fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.17,0:08:39.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Asagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.53,0:08:44.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This is creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:47.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,My body was just taken over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:49.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I was too careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:51.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:54.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, enough. I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:57.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll leave once you can play the koto, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.02,0:08:58.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:02.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we have to start by making the koto?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.78,0:09:06.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, since it's a special koto after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:10.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an Ayakashi called senbiki that looks like a carp with a white string in its body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:12.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we're going to catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:15.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So why do we need to catch a fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:19.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Stop complaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:21.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that gloomy face?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.82,0:09:24.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:38.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:40.75,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive us, Natsume-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:40.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:42.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.79,0:09:48.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of relationship do you and Bullseye have?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:53.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:57.15,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:59.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He was an umbrella holder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:01.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Umbrella holder?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:09.36,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,In Isozuki Forest, those with talent would come to calm the forest where the god Mibu-sama lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:15.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There would be those who held umbrellas for Mibu-sama and the others there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:20.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullseye's duty was to protect everyone as a bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.81,0:10:24.46,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He is very skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:42.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Isozuki was a beautiful place, much like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:45.75,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to always be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.75,0:10:49.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I would always live by Mibu-sama's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:51.46,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:53.61,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:59.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But he banished you because you couldn't play anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.24,0:11:02.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What a small-minded god.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:04.42,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Natsume-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.42,0:11:08.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Mibu-sama picked me up because I didn't have my own place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:13.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran away because I couldn't stand being useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:18.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I got one! It's a senbiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:22.67,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:28.42,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,See? This is used for the string.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.42,0:11:31.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So is this all we need for materials?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:32.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:34.42,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.78,0:11:35.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:37.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to search for a tree stump.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.51,0:11:42.93,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's got to be one with bamboo shoots that have just started growing out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:52.95,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A little longer... A little longer and you can play.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:02.42,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullseye, really... {supposed to imply his love for Asagi, but english sentences are not backwards like jap}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:11.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you get so wet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:12.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.76,0:12:14.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I need to get you a towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:16.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Takashi-kun might catch a cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.81,0:12:17.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:20.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:22.92,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, dry yourself thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.92,0:12:25.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Your nose is all wet too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:28.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I was always there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:30.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:35.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Go take a bath, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:36.92,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It just heated up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:38.63,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get in, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:42.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,How long will I be able to stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:16.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.68,0:13:18.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Asagi's?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:21.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullseye...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:23.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You've awoken, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:26.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but Asagi's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.89,0:13:27.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:30.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Asagi's fingers can no longer play the koto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:35.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She has a sickness where her body dries up like dirt and crumbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:37.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She can't go back to being normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:42.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,However, while she is in another body, its progression will slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:45.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful to you, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:54.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The last time I saw her laugh was when she happily played her instrument for Mibu-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.88,0:13:56.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And during her performance...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.41,0:14:01.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,her body suddenly began to crumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:08.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Her white slender fingers and her bright cheeks were lost before her admired Mibu-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:12.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow is a full moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:15.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The path to Isozuki will open for a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:20.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I want her to play before Mibu-sama, even if only once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.16,0:14:24.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help us until then, Natsume-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:27.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing this, Bullseye?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:30.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you go so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:34.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.99,0:14:47.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Akagane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:49.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.39,0:14:52.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just an umbrella holder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:15:01.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I just can't find one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.93,0:15:03.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.72,0:15:05.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't find any.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:09.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it even here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:19.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you looking for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:21.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A tree stump with a bamboo shoot growing out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:24.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one in that thicket over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.56,0:15:28.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, there it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:31.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What was I talking with just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.04,0:15:33.91,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you. I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:37.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange, I will have your guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:42.46,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I talked with some weird Youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:47.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Natsume! Are you even looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:52.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Natsume! This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:56.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, time to start carving it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:05.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm feeling sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:10.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this feverish pain Asagi's?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:14.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If she performs when she's this weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:16.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Her life will...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.30,0:16:19.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:23.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry you have to go through this because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:26.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I haven't confirmed this with you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:27.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:31.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to play the koto too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:34.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were given...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:40.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were given that chance once more, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:46.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not dexterous and I have stiff fingers, so you might not be able to play well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:47.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that still okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:50.61,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:06.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Asagi, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:12.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Akagane always, always...{loved you}{again he's implying love just like the other line but doesn't actually say it}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.56,0:17:20.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! Wake up, Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:22.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:25.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We can still make it. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:30.36,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Akagane? What is it? What's going-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:35.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Asagi, the path to Isozuki is still open right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:38.74,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Go and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:39.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:43.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We promised! I'm here for your guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:44.90,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The one from before!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:53.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Akagane...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:00.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:04.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The koto is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:08.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Asagi's... Bullseye's... precious...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:11.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:18.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:20.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:23.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:24.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.03,0:18:27.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I chased him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:29.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,How about the koto?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:33.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's safe. You protected it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:35.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.77,0:18:38.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Think you can stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:40.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We can make it if we hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:42.67,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't, I'll carry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:45.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Bullseye? You can't go with those wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:47.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.36,0:18:51.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:19:02.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that if it were possible, I would like to play once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.84,0:19:08.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I always, always played only for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:10.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:15.25,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could play once more,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:18.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,it would be for my kind and precious friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:22.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to play for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:26.59,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you listen, Akagane?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:48.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I could hear music from far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:52.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A beautiful sound that I had never heard before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.39,0:19:56.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, that sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:02.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,came from my fingers and made the air vibrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.76,0:20:30.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Asagi left my body as if she was falling towards the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:35.33,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:37.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,0:20:39.62,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take Asagi and return to my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:41.13,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.91,0:20:48.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just in a deep, deep sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:50.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:53.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Asagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.68,0:20:56.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Bullseye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:20:57.55,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:21:01.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.29,0:21:09.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you go when I was in trouble, sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:11.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel better now, nice guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:14.33,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry. Buy me some steamed buns.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:16.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanatsuji isn't open yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.34,0:21:17.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.24,0:21:23.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there a place where you wanted to be forever, Nyanko-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:27.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't ever need that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:30.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:34.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I always thought, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.49,0:21:36.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Idiot! Don't hug me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.41,0:21:37.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.29,0:21:42.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to play on what they left behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.11,0:21:45.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,but that beautiful sound never came from it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.77,0:21:52.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That sound didn't come from my fingers, but played through her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:54.74,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Breakfast is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.74,0:21:55.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
